    <item>
      <title>汉莎航空在票价战和商务旅行减少的情况下削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/lufthansa-slashes-costs-to-adjust-to-business-travel-weakness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一封致员工的信函显示，由于商务旅行减少和竞争加剧的“新现实”导致票价从疫情后的高位下降，汉莎航空计划大幅削减成本并削减未来项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/lufthansa-slashes-costs-to-adjust-to-business-travel-weakness</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 15:29:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚最高法院撤销对力拓锂项目的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/serbia-s-top-court-rules-against-rio-tinto-s-lithium-project-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚宪法法院推翻了一项政府法令，该法令在政治争议和环保人士的抗议中于 2022 年突然阻止了力拓集团在该国价值 24 亿美元的锂项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/serbia-s-top-court-rules-against-rio-tinto-s-lithium-project-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 14:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
